                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The comments are wrong -- it's actually \"isChecked()\". The method name was chosen to be consistent with the API of the radio and checkbox elements.",
