                    "body": "Two things:\r\n\r\n1. I need to set value and label to have same value:\r\n\r\n)->addElement(\r\n            'button',\r\n            'trash',\r\n            array(\r\n                'label' => '<span class=\"ui-icon ui-icon-trash\">&nbsp;<\/span>Trash',\r\n                'value' => '<span class=\"ui-icon ui-icon-trash\">&nbsp;<\/span>Trash'\r\n            )\r\n        );\r\n\r\n2. isChecked returns false when button is clicked, and true if it's not!?!?",
